    h6 Engineering of Software Subsystems
    p I learned about software architecture and design patterns in object oriented systems. Each class we would learn about a different design pattern and do an exercise related to it. The first group project for the class was to design and implement a desktop application for managing stocks using design patterns such as composite, and command. The second group project was to take an existing desktop application that was written without any design patterns in mind and refactor a part of it to be much cleaner using a design pattern. We chose to use the state pattern to represent a frame as part of the scoring system.
